U INFORMATION U

Skullgirls is a fast-paced 2-D fighting game that puts players in
control of fierce warriors in an extraordinary Dark Deco world
Featuring all-new game systems which test the skills of veteran
fighting game fans while also making the genre enjoyable and
accessible to newcomers. Skullgirls is a modern take on classic
arcade fighters with a hand-drawn high-definition twist. It's a
one-of-a-kind, action-packed competition complete with awesome
combos and an intriguing backstory
